data.description: If you're looking for a fully finished character home in established neighborhood near downtown & island park you need to check this one out! The home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a 2 stall detached garage. Main level features living room, extra area that can be used as an office, kitchen, dining space, and a bathroom conveniently located nearby. Second floor includes all three bedrooms. Basement has 2 stairways, tons of storage room, family room that features cast iron gas fireplace + extended area with endless opportunity, laundry with utility sink and a full bathroom! Outside you will find newer deck on front of house, & large patio area ready for you to relax and enjoy! Get your showing scheduled TODAY!
